source: La Grădiniţa cu Program Prelungit „Pinocchio” din Fălticeni a avut loc joi, 7 noiembrie, premierea concursului „Talente la ornamente”.
target: The "Pinocchio" Extended Program Kindergarten in Fălticeni hosted the awards ceremony for the "Talente la ornamente" (Talents in Ornaments) competition on Thursday, November 7th.
